metadata.description: The third brother in the Goblin group, it will attack with its brothers. Its weapon is an axe. As an ancient family, Its nature is very naughty and evil. Because it is not big, it can't cause great damage when it is alone. Once they're united, the destructive power can not be underestimated.

Its soul has been manipulated by the devil. It's intimate with Deviruchies and did many bad things. In the depths of its fallen heart, it's always looking for the answer to a question - what is the bottom line?

card_data.name: Deviling Card
card_data.effect: Neutral Dmg Taken -50%,  Other Dmg Taken from Other Attributes ＋50%

Because it is not big, it can't cause great damage when it is alone. Once they're united, the destructive power can not be underestimated.

Perching in Underwater Caves, Its body is like an rubber, and its skin is tender. As a well-known ornamental monster on the seabed, it is very enthusiastic to tourists. From time to time, it will give a passionate embrace, but because it's too close with humans, it has been warned many times by the Monsters Association.

A special type converted from some of Poring souls, which Ghost element annoys many players. It appears and disappears mysteriously and elusive, seems that it's looking for something to end its regret.

card_data.name: Ghosting Card
card_data.effect: Turn the armor's element into Ghost, HP Regen -50%

metadata.description: An aquatic monster with high defense. They often appear in the Underwater Caves in groups and love boxing. Don't provoke them, otherwise you can't afford to receive double hard blows.

The king of Thief Bugs, with a very fast speed and a high attack. However, the braves who had the strength once party up and went to eliminate it. It's said that you will get a lot of gold after defeating it.

card_data.name: Golden Thief Bug Card
card_data.effect: All Magic Dmg Taken -50%, SP cost of skill use ＋100%

metadata.description: A monster that appears in the deep sea. It's named for its extending sword-shaped upper jaw. When swimming, its strong and powerful tail can produce a huge driving force. The long spear-like jaw plays the role of splitting water. Its hard upper jaw can pierce the thick bottom of the ship.

An evolutionary version of Roda Frog. It has been keen to listen to all kinds of programs of Midgard since it inadvertently obtained a radio left by humans. Occasionally when you get close to it, You can still hear that it is seriously practicing talk shows.

A semi-fish and semi-human monster that appears in the depths of the Underwater Caves. They're very gentle and united and friendly to each other. Due to the overexploitation of the ocean by humans and the impact of the seabed seal, the ecological environment has been deteriorating and some of them have been washed into the sewers.

The fourth brother in the Goblin group, it will attack with its brothers. Its weapon is a hammer. As an ancient family, Its nature is very naughty and evil. Because it is not big, it can't cause great damage when it is alone. Once they're united, the destructive power can not be underestimated.

Before his death, he was a brave and fearless warrior. After his resurrection, he was once lost the desire to survive again. After chatting with the Porings, he found new goals and started to work hard to warm up and prepare to participate in the monster sprint relay!

card_data.name: Skeleton Card
card_data.effect: auto attack has a 3% chance to stun the target for 5 seconds
